                                @{B} ABOUT @{UB}
 Vinfo is short for "Visual Info" and was written for low price Amigas such
 as Amiga 1200, and should result in the the minimum price for a simple non 
 interactive info system that can handle both text and graphics in an 
 extremely simple way. Anyone can use Vinfo, even my mum !

 Vinfo is using PAL/NTSC low resolution since the idea was (is !) that it 
 could be used in any sort of small locale installation like in:

       *  supermarkets
       *  hotells
       *  exhibitions
       *  locale cable tv.  

       etc...

 In case of "anything" please do contact the @{" Author " link Author} !

@ENDNODE
