@NEXT Function
@PREV MAIN
@TOC MAIN

                                @{B} INSTALL  @{UB}
 You need an Amiga with OS3.0 system or better  , no more no less !
 Vinfo is 100% system friendly and for a list of what is required from
 the system see @{" System resources used " link System}



 There is no INSTALL script since Vinfo is not a utility program.
 
 Start Vinfo from SHELL or WB ,  you only need the VINFO exe file ,whatever
 it is called, for a quick start,  just click on the Icon in the extracted
 archive , under Vinfo/ and voila , Vinfo comes up with a demo text.
  

@ENDNODE
