      * topaz.font     11
      * helvetica.font 15
      * sapphire.font  14
      * ruby.font      15
      * garnet.font    9

 Datatypes:
      The more datatypes the better !, but to include graphics in Vinfo 
      you need the corresponding datatype for the graphic format.

 ram disk:
	yes , the ram: is used , but only at startup .
